# TDD at All Levels

ALWAYS use TDD at ALL levels — unit, integration, AND E2E. Write tests FIRST.
Red → Green → Refactor is mandatory. If tests lag behind code at ANY level, TDD was not followed.

See `.agent/directives/testing-strategy.md` for the full testing strategy.
